  "texts": [
    "Particularly, 14.9% of the questions in the RD Exam are at the Expert level.",
    "However, as reported by Rein et al.",
    "49, the GPQA questions are \"extremely difficult, \"from which PhD students achieved a 65% score while non-expert individuals achieved a 34% score.",
    "Moreover, DROP 51 demonstrated that Claude 3.5 with Three Shot prompting outperformed in reasoning over text.",
    "Conversely, our results indicated that GPT-4o performed better using the reasoning process of CoT prompting."
